products.title: Goccia Rain Jacket
products.description: Don’t let a little sprinkle stop your ride. Just pull on the Castelli Goccia Rain Jacket and get after it. Waterproof, breathable Torrent fabric keeps you dry while a back vent helps the heat escape. Reflective Castelli graphics make you more visible when riding in traffic.
products.shortDescription: Don’t let a little sprinkle stop your ride. Just pull on the Castelli Men’s Goccia Rain Jacket and get after it.

products.title: Northwall Jacket - Men's
products.description: Pack the Patagonia Northwall Jacket when you are planning a trip to Big Sky country. The mountains up there in Montana were not made for the weak of heart, and damn it gets chilly and windy. The Northwall is lined with R4 fleece to provide high warmth-to-weight ratio so you can scale the major peaks.
products.shortDescription: Pack the Patagonia Northwall Jacket when you are planning a trip to Big Sky country.
bulletPoints: Water-resistant Polar Tec Pro fabric provides protection from wet weather and extreme mountain winds and provides great stretch for making the next big move
The grid design of the Regulator R4 fleece provides warmth and wicks sweat
Sonic welded seam construction with reinforced stitching eliminates bulky seams
Two-way adjustable helmet-compatible hood with a laminated visor to direct rain and snow away from your face in inclement weather
Modified Y-joint sleeve construction for overhead mobility without jacket lifting at the waist
Cord locks in the hood and hem to seal out rain and snow
Recyclable through Patagonia’s Common Threads Garment recycling program

products.title: Vaporshell Jacket - Women's
products.description: Never question whether or not to pack a rainshell again—the Stoic Women’s Vaporshell Jacket protects like an atmosphere when you wear it, but weighs as much as an apparition when you have it in your pack. This lightweight, waterproof, extremely packable rainshell puts all your past rain gear to shame.
products.shortDescription: Never question whether or not to pack a rainshell again—the Stoic Women’s Vaporshell Jacket protects like an atmosphere when you wear it, but weighs as much as an apparition when you have it in your pack.
bulletPoints: Lightweight VaporShell shuns rain and vents body heat like none other
3-D Ergonomic fit moves with you, not against you
Extremely compressible—plays nice with other gear in your pack
Stoic Vaporshell fabric’s air permeability and vapor permeability is so shocking, you’ll swear it's magic

products.title: Bombshell Jacket - Men's
products.description: A tried-and-true workhorse among storm shells, the Stoic Men's Bombshell Jacket allows Utah Avalanche Center forecasters, ski photographers, and outdoor professionals thrive amidst Old Man Winter's brutal assault. You might have a closet full of jackets designed for foul weather, but this jacket's three-layer, highly-waterproof breathable fabric makes those other jackets worthy of the yard sale. Fully-welded seam construction, underarm vents for comfort, a Recco reflector for safety, and a generous, ultra-mobile fit set the Bombshell apart in a mountainous arena where details matter. Set your sights on the mountains and let this uncompromising hardshell handle the rest.
products.shortDescription: A tried-and-true workhorse among storm shells, the Stoic Men's Bombshell Jacket allows Utah Avalanche Center forecasters, ski photographers, and outdoor professionals thrive amidst Old Man Winter's brutal assault.
bulletPoints: 3-Layer Bombshell fabric offers 20K-rated weatherproof protection and supreme breathability so you're comfortable, not stifled, underneath this shell
Mechanical stretch fabric construction keeps this shell flexible so your mobility isn't hindered when you're fully-layered and battened down
Fully-welded seams increase the Bombshell’s durability over standard taped-seam shell
Mesh-lined underarm vents banish excess body heat during long boot packs
3-D ergonomic fit offers uninhibited mobility without drowning you in excess fabric—if you tend to like a roomier fit, size up
Recco reflector in the upper arm aids Recco-equipped search and rescue parties should disaster strike and you require rescue
Removable powder skirt and wrist gaiters complete the seal from the elements
Backcountry.com is the exclusive US distributor for Stoic products

products.title: Resolve Jacket - Men's
products.description: If you live in a place where every day is clear, blue, and perfect, don’t bother looking at this jacket. Those of us who live on Earth may want to check out The North Face Men’s Resolve Jacket. The North Face used HyVent, a waterproof and breathable fabric, to make the Resolve as comfortable as possible on the days where the sun doesn’t make an appearance.
products.shortDescription: The North Face used HyVent, a waterproof and breathable fabric, to make the Resolve as comfortable as possible on the days where the sun doesn’t make an appearance.
bulletPoints: Fully adjustable rain hood stows away into the collar
Mesh lined for increased breathability
Brushed collar lining feels soft against your face

products.title: Metropolis Parka - Women's
products.description: Some mornings the wind comes whipping through the buildings like a runaway subway train. It’s a good thing that you have The North Face Women’s Metropolis Parka to hold back the onslaught. With head-to-knees windproof protection and 600-fill down insulation, the Metropolis can keep that nasty wind at bay.
products.shortDescription: With head-to-knees windproof protection and 600-fill down insulation, The North Face Women's Metropolis Down Parka can keep that nasty wind at bay.
bulletPoints: Classic style to keep you looking good while you stay warm
Long parka cut to keep you toasty from the top of your head to the top of your boots
Removable hood adds versatility for changing weather conditions
Snap and zip front closure gives you an extra layer of windproof protection at the zipper
Internal security pocket fends off baddies

products.title: Denali Fleece Jacket - Men's
products.description: Already a classic, The North Face's warm, versatile Men's Denali Fleece Jacket is now constructed entirely from recycled and Bluesign-certified materials. You can enjoy its four-season fleecy goodness even more knowing it required less fuel and produced fewer greenhouse gases before getting to you.
products.shortDescription: Already a classic, The North Face's warm, versatile Men's Denali Fleece Jacket is now constructed entirely from recycled and Bluesign-certified materials.
bulletPoints: Two chest pockets and two hand-warmer pockets provide plenty of storage for essentials cell phone to ski straps
Underarm vents help you stay comfortable when you’re working up a sweat breaking trail
Abrasion patches on chest, shoulders, and arms block wind and guard against pack straps and ski edges
Hem cinch cord blocks out drafts
Zip-in compatible, so you can layer it with a The North Face shell for the ultimate cold-busting comfort

products.title: Resolve Jacket - Women's
products.description:
Fend off torrential downpours thanks to The North Face Resolve Jacket. Waterproof and breathable HyVent 2L shell fabric allows sweaty vapor to escape from within, and shrugs off heinous weather on the outside. At less than 17 ounces this jacket packs easily without weighing you down on long treks. An interior mesh lining provides a buffer between your under layers and the outer fabric, and a hem cinch cord battens down the waist. Flip up the adjustable hood when the skies turn particularly nasty, but don't worry; fully-taped seams add an additional measure of weatherproofing so you won't spring any unexpected leaks.

 The North Face used a fully adjustable hood to round out the Resolve Rain Jacket's features and ensure you stay bone-dry even in nasty weather.
products.shortDescription: Fend off torrential downpours thanks to The North Face Resolve Jacket. Waterproof and breathable HyVent 2L shell fabric allows sweaty vapor to escape from within, and shrugs off heinous weather on the outside.

products.title: Amongstit Jacket - Men's
products.description: You just woke up from the best dream of your entire life. Perfect virgin snow, lifts without lines, T-shirt weather, and a hottie-liftie with a beer waiting for you every time you come around. Get out of bed, towel yourself off, and high-tail it to the hill. But since it was just a fantasy, grab your Amongstit Jacket from The North Face and make your dream a reality. High-tech fabrics keep you warm and dry even if the weather isn’t perfect, and with all of those pockets, you can pack enough booze for you and your fave liftie. Hopefully that part wasn’t just a dream.
products.shortDescription: Grab your Amongstit Jacket from The North Face and make your dream a reality.
bulletPoints: The HyVent shell handles flurries and breathes so excess heat doesn’t get trapped
Full underarm zip-vents allow you dump excess heat while you are punishing the mountain
Heatseeker Eco insulation uses recycled material to keep things easy on the environment
Detachable powder skirt with gripper elastic keeps the cold off of your backside
Removable faux-fur hood lining for extra warmth and a bit of class

products.title: Venture Jacket - Women's
products.description: You're five miles from camp when you here the roll of thunder and see black clouds descending from above the canyon. It's going to rain, and it's going to rain hard. Pull The North Face Women's Venture Jacket from it's compact pocket and let it's ultra-high-tech fabric keep you dry when the storm hits.
bulletPoints: HyVent 2.5L EC seals out rain while encouraging water vapor to escape so you stay dry without that muggy feeling
Hook-and-loop storm flap and cuffs create a next-to-skin barrier against the elements
Adjustable hood has a hidden drawcord to help you get a perfect fit
Packable design lets you stuff and store this jacket into one of its own pockets
so you always have it when you need it
